{
  "stem": "11611.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That's not quite accurate, but that's roughly the scale.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Otto Ohlendorf was head of the Einsatzgruppen, Now, you may not know what a Einsatzgruppen group is.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, let's assume you do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I would translate it roughly as SS murder squads.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was their duty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I suppose he was instrumental in killing about 200,000 or 300,000 people in the fields-- these were the detachments that machine gunned people, men women, and children over open pits so they could bury them easily.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He got a death sentence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But a lot of people who were involved in miscellaneous murders here and there just got terms, were out of jail about as fast as I got back to the States.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, it was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I ought to amplify that a little.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While I was there, at the end of the trials, I was there practically to the very end.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the cases were all concluded, and I was just loafing around-- I was entitled to about two months compensatory leave time, because I hadn't taken all that much leave.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He must have been 80 years old at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a stateless Jew from Freiburg, who had been a professor of languages at a German university, and who was used by a bunch of Jewish DP's for currency transactions.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He could legally deal in script and American money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The DP's were prohibited.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were kind of connivers, and managed to secure a lot of script.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was able to convert it for them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I finally relented, and I took on the defense of this guy-- who was, as I say, stateless.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a court trial by the occupation court.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not a court martial.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
